      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total showstopper. This beauty is in truly pristine condition\u2014it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous with maintenance, so there\u2019s not a scratch or a smudge to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for a new home. You really have to see it in person to believe how gorgeous it is. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
