      "description": "This 2021 Porsche 718 Cayman is the definition of a 'time capsule' vehicle. Finished in a stunning Jet Black Metallic, the exterior remains in showroom condition with a deep, mirror-like shine thanks to a professional ceramic coating. There are absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin retains that fresh-from-the-factory scent; the black leather sport seats show zero bolster wear, and the dashboard is pristine. Mechanically, it is flawless, having been meticulously maintained at the dealership with a full service history available. Always garaged under a soft cover and never driven in inclement weather, this car is for the collector who demands perfection. Low miles, two keys, and all original documentation included.",
